name: WestJet NEW LIVERY Boeing 737 MAX 8 First Ever Landing at Calgary Airport
description:
Last month, WestJet revealed a new livery and brand identity in preparation for the delivery of their first Boeing 787 in 2019, and will be slowly rolling out the new livery on their existing aircraft. In the meantime, all new 737 MAX deliveries will have the new paint job, and this is the very first aircraft to wear this sharp looking livery. I personally love it, I think WestJet nailed it with this new look! ATC is included, hope you enjoy the new livery landing at WestJet's home base of Calgary International Airport for the first time!

Thanks for watching!
